initialize (private)

initialize: function(json)

Initializes the plugin.  Implicitly calls SSRegisterPlugin as well as subclass’s setup method.

serverCall

serverCall: function(method,
params,
callback)

Allows a plugin to make a server call.

Parameters

methodthe method name to call.
paramsthe url parameters to be passed in.
callbackthe function to called when server call is complete.

SSGetShifts

Returns an array of shift properties

Parameters

shiftIdsan array of ids.
callBacka function to be called when the shifts have been grabbed.
errorHandlera function to be called if the operation fails.
